revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== From ''[[Xanthochroi]]''. ===Pronunciation=== * {{IPA|en|/zænˈθəʊkɹɔɪd/}} ===Adjective=== {{en-adj}} # {{lb|en|anthropology}} Pertaining to the [[Xanthochroi]]; having fair [[hair]] and a pale [[complexion]]. ===Noun=== {{en-noun}} # {{lb|en|anthropology}} A member of the [[Xanthochroi]].
